### ============================================
### 서비스 헬스 체크
### ============================================


### ------------------------------------------
### Spring Boot 서비스 헬스 체크
### ------------------------------------------

### Flight Service (8080)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Ticket Service (8081)
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Payment Service (8082)
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Reservation Service (8083)
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/health
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### 인프라 서비스 헬스 체크
### ------------------------------------------

### Elasticsearch 클러스터 상태
GET http://localhost:9200/_cluster/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Jaeger Query 서비스 목록
GET http://localhost:16686/api/services
Accept: application/json

###

### Jaeger 최근 트레이스 조회 (reservation 서비스)
GET http://localhost:16686/api/traces?service=reservation&limit=10
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### Actuator 엔드포인트
### ------------------------------------------

### Flight - 전체 Actuator 정보
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator
Accept: application/json

###

### Reservation - Circuit Breaker 상태
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/circuitbreakers
Accept: application/json

###

### Reservation - Circuit Breaker 이벤트
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/circuitbreakerevents
Accept: application/json
